rity access to activities','Enjoy door-to-door pickup and drop-off in a shared 4-wheel drive vehicle (Land Cruiser or similar)','2025-03-01',150,'active'),(13,'Private Vehicle','2-7 Guest ','Enjoy door-to-door pickup and drop-off in a private 4-wheel drive vehicle (Land Cruiser or similar) for up to 7 people.','2025-03-01',850,'active'),(14,'Self Drive','Arrive at the meeting point in your own vehicle','Experience the magic of the desert with our Overnight Desert Safari Self-Drive package. Drive your own vehicle to the desert meeting point.','2025-03-01',140,'active'),(15,'4*4 Pick & Drop','door-to-door pickup and drop-off','Enjoy door-to-door pickup and drop-off in a shared 4-wheel drive vehicle (Land Cruiser or similar)','2025-03-01',240,'active'),(16,'Normal Package','Pick & Drop by Van/Mini Van','Enjoy the highlights of Dubai with our convenient bus pick-up and drop-off service from common locations. Explore the city\'s must-see attractions comfortably and efficiently.','2025-03-01',55,'active'),(17,'Premium Package','Pick & Drop by 4-wheel drive','Enjoy the convenience of home pick-up and drop-off service in a comfortable 7-seater vehicle.','2025-03-01',79,'active'),(18,'Shared vehicle','Pick & Drop by Van/Mini Van','Discover the beauty of Abu Dhabi with our convenient sharing pick-up service. Explore the city\'s top attractions.','2025-03-01',120,'active'),(19,'Private Vehicle','2-7 Guest ','Discover the beauty of Abu Dhabi with our exclusive private pick-up service in a comfortable vehicle. Enjoy a personalized tour of the city\'s top attractions.','2025-03-01',750,'active'),(21,'Normal Package','Mountain tour','Explore the stunning landscapes of Hatta with our guided tour. Visit the Hatta Dam, ancient forts, and picturesque oases.','2025-03-02',90,'active'),(22,'Premium Package','Mountain tour & Dune Bashing','Discover the natural beauty and thrilling adventures of Hatta with our guided tour. Begin with an exhilarating dune bashing experience, followed by visits to the Hatta Dam, ancient forts, and picturesque oases.','2025-03-02',150,'active'),(23,'Normal Package','Bus pickup from designated pickup points','Embark on an exciting desert safari adventure with quad biking. Enjoy a convenient bus pick-up, thrilling dune bashing, and an exhilarating quad bike ride.','2025-03-02',125,'active'),(24,'Premium Package','Pick & Drop by 4-wheel drive	','Experience the thrill of a desert safari with quad biking and 4x4 pick-up. Adventure awaits!','2025-03-02',225,'active');
