INSERT INTO `faqs` VALUES (1,'What is Desert Safari Dubai ?','Desert Safari Dubai is a safari tour in Dubai desert with wonderful red sand dunes with the sunrise and sunset view that remains in your memory lifetime. ',1,'2025-04-08 21:26:08'),(2,'What is included in the Desert Safari Dubai package?','Our packages include activities such as Dune Bashing, Buggy Rides, Quad Bike adventures, and more. We also offer a Pick and Drop facility for a hassle-free experience.',1,'2025-04-08 21:35:46'),(3,'What should I wear for a desert safari?','Comfortable and breathable clothing is recommended, along with sunglasses, a hat, and sunscreen. Avoid high heels, as you\'ll be walking on sand.',1,'2025-04-08 21:36:03'),(4,'Is the Morning Desert Safari suitable for families?','Yes, our Morning Desert Safari is ideal for families, offering gentle activities as well as adventurous options like Dune Bashing.',1,'2025-04-08 21:36:26'),(5,'What makes the Luxury Desert Safari special?','The Luxury Desert Safari includes exclusive services like private vehicles, gourmet dining, and access to premium campsites for an unforgettable experience.',1,'2025-04-08 21:36:42'),(6,'Can I customize my desert safari experience?','Absolutely! Whether you\'re looking for VIP treatment or a focus on certain activities, we’re happy to tailor your adventure.',1,'2025-04-08 21:36:59'),(7,'Are children allowed to participate in dune bashing?','Yes, but for safety reasons, dune bashing is recommended for children aged 6 and above. We can adjust the ride\'s intensity as needed.',1,'2025-04-08 21:37:16'),(8,'What safety measures are in place for 4 x 4 Desert Safaris?','Our vehicles are equipped with all necessary safety features, and our drivers are trained professionals experienced in desert terrains.',1,'2025-04-08 21:37:31'),(9,'Do you offer photography services during the tours?','Yes, we have professional photographers available to capture your memories amidst the stunning desert landscape.',1,'2025-04-08 21:38:01'),(10,'Can we book tours to Dubai attractions along with a desert safari?','Certainly! We offer combined Dubai Tours packages that include visits to major Dubai Attractions along with your desert adventure.',1,'2025-04-08 21:38:18'),(11,'How can I book a buggy ride or quad bike adventure?',' How can I book a buggy ride or quad bike adventure?',1,'2025-04-08 21:38:36'),(12,'What is Desert Safari Dubai’s cancellation policy?','   Our cancellation policy is designed to be fair while accounting for operational commitments:  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. <strong>Refund Eligibility</strong>:  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>24 hours before safari Timing</strong>  <br>\r\n    <br>\r\n\r\n2. <strong>Rescheduling</strong>:  <br>\r\n  ✅ Free rescheduling up to <strong>24 hours prior</strong> (subject to availability).  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n3. <strong>Weather Cancellations</strong>:  <br>\r\n  ✅ If <strong>we</strong> cancel due to sandstorms extreme weather:<br>  \r\n     - Choice of <strong>full refund if paid</strong> or <strong>free rescheduling</strong>.  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n4. <strong>Refund Processing</strong>:  <br>\r\n  ✅ Processed in <strong>5–7 business days</strong> to the original payment method.  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n5. Special Cases<br>\r\n  ✅ Medical emergencies (with documentation): Case-by-case review for partial refunds.  \r\n',1,'2025-04-17 01:48:21'),(13,'What is Desert Safari Dubai\'s age policy for tours and activities?','Our age guidelines prioritize safety while ensuring all guests can enjoy the desert experience:  <br>\r\n\r\n1. <strong>General Safari Participation</strong>:  <br>\r\n   ✅ All ages welcome for standard morning evening safaris  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Children under 5</strong>: Must be accompanied by parents at all times  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n2. <strong>Adventure Activity Restrictions</strong>:  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Dune bashing</strong>: Minimum For All  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Quad biking</strong>: 6+ years   <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Sandboarding</strong>: For All  <br>\r\n<br>\r\n3. <strong>Pricing for Children</strong>:  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>0–3 years</strong>: Free (must be declared during booking)  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>3+</strong>: Full adult pricing.  <br>\r\n\r\n4. <strong>Special Cases</strong>:  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Senior citizens</strong>: Recommended for safaris consult a doctor if pre-existing conditions exist and inform us earlier.  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Pregnant women</strong>: Permitted in camps but prohibited from dune bashing.  <br>\r\n   ✅ <strong>Guests with disabilities</strong>: Contact us for accessible arrangements.  <br>',1,'2025-04-17 01:55:26');
