INSERT INTO `package_content` VALUES (375,11,'Tour Description','Drive your car to our desert meeting point and begin an exciting desert safari Dubai adventure packed with unforgettable moments! Experience the thrill of a 4x4 dune drive over the sands. Hop on an Arabian camel for a fun ride and try your hand at sandboarding with a quick lesson. Don\'t miss the magical sunset—it\'s a view you\'ll treasure forever.\r\nAfter the adventure, head to a welcoming desert camp for a delicious BBQ dinner paired with soft drinks. Relax with Hubble bubble and enjoy mesmerizing live performances, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, a fiery fire show, the elegant silk show, and traditional acts like Ayala and Dabka. You can even get beautiful henna designs from a talented local artist. Throughout the experience, our friendly and expert driver/guide will ensure everything runs smoothly and stress-free.'),(376,11,'Highlights','<ul><li><p>Thrilling 4x4 dune drive across the iconic red dunes of Dubai. </p></li><li><p>Enjoy a camel ride and learn the basics of sandboarding. </p></li><li><p>Take in breathtaking sunset views—a perfect photo opportunity. </p></li><li><p>Relax at a cozy desert camp and savor a mouthwatering BBQ dinner. </p></li><li><p>Refresh with soft drinks while enjoying the vibrant camp atmosphere. </p></li><li><p>Experience captivating live performances, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, fire shows, silk shows, Ayala, and Dabka. </p></li><li><p>Get a stunning henna hand painting from a local artist. Unwind with shisha as you immerse yourself in the cultural and traditional vibes.</p></li></ul><p></p>'),(377,11,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.'),(384,15,'Full description','Step into a world of relaxation and charm with our Dhow Cruise Marina—a perfect escape into Dubai’s sparkling waters. For two serene hours, you’ll glide through the Marina, surrounded by jaw-dropping views of landmarks like the Palm Jumeirah, Atlantis, and Burj Al Arab.\r\nFrom the moment you step aboard, it’s all about comfort and good vibes. We’ll greet you with a welcome drink. Whether you’re on the cool, cozy lower deck with air conditioning or on the breezy, open upper deck, you’re in for an unforgettable ride. Then, the fun begins; dig into a delicious 5-star buffet dinner with options for vegetarians and non-vegetarians alike, paired with unlimited juice, tea, and coffee to keep the evening flowing.\r\nEntertainment adds to the magic, with live Tanoura dance performances and soothing background music in English, Arabic, and Hindi to suit all tastes. Need some quiet time? The upper deck has a smoking area to unwind, while separate restrooms for men and women keep things convenient and stress-free.\r\nAs you soak in the stunning views and enjoy the breeze, this cruise offers a perfect mix of great food, amazing entertainment and picture-perfect moments. It’s more than just a trip—it’s a celebration of everything that makes Dubai unforgettable.'),(385,15,'Highlights','Two-hour luxury cruise along Dubai Marina’s sparkling waters.\r\nBreathtaking views of the Palm Jumeirah, Atlantis, and Burj Al Arab.\r\nDelicious 5-star international buffet dinner with vegetarian and non-vegetarian options.\r\nUnlimited refreshments, including juice, tea, coffee, and soft drinks.\r\nLive entertainment featuring the mesmerizing Tanoura dance show.\r\nRelaxing background music in English, Arabic, and Hindi.\r\nFully air-conditioned lower deck and open-air upper deck for your comfort.'),(386,15,'Key Tips','Arrive at the marina early to avoid any rush and enjoy the boarding experience.\r\nDress in light and breathable clothes for maximum comfort on both the lower and upper decks.\r\nMake the most of unlimited refreshments like juice, tea, coffee, and soft drinks throughout the cruise.\r\nBring a camera or phone to capture stunning views of Dubai’s iconic landmarks, including Palm Jumeirah, Atlantis, and Burj Al Arab.\r\nTake in the vibrant live Tanoura dance performance and background music for a magical vibe.\r\nSmokers can unwind in the designated smoking area on the upper deck.\r\nExplore both the air-conditioned lower deck and the open-air upper deck for different perspectives of the cruise.\r\nSeparate restroom facilities for men and women ensure a hassle-free and comfortable experience.'),(387,17,'Tour Description','Imagine spending two peaceful hours sailing through Dubai Creek, surrounded by stunning views of Bur Dubai and the timeless charm of the city. This isn’t just a cruise—it’s a chance to relax, enjoy, and soak in the beauty of old Dubai.\r\nFrom the moment you step on board, you’re treated like a VIP. A warm welcome , with refreshing soft drinks, mineral water, and juice, to get your evening started. Whether you chill out in the cozy, air-conditioned lower deck or enjoy the breeze on the open-air upper deck, every spot is perfect for taking in the sights.\r\nDinner is something special—an amazing buffet with international flavors, offering options for both vegetarians and non-vegetarians. And the best part? You can pair it with unlimited drinks, including tea, coffee, juices, and soft drinks—it’s all there for you.\r\nThe entertainment is a feast for the senses! Watch the mesmerizing Tanoura dance, marvel at a fun magic show, and groove to live music that sets the mood just right. Smokers can unwind at the upper deck’s designated area, while separate restrooms for men and women make sure everyone’s comfortable.\r\nAs you cruise along, the calm waters, delicious food, and lively performances come together to create an evening you’ll never forget. Whether you’re snapping photos of the amazing views or simply enjoying the moment, this is an experience full of unforgettable memories.\r\nAnd here\'s one without the pick and drop service:\r\n\r\n\"Experience the charm of Dubai\'s historic Creek with our Dhow Cruise. Enjoy a scenic sail, stunning skyline views, and a delightful onboard dining experience. Perfect for an unforgettable evening in the heart of the city.'),(388,17,'Highlights','Two-hour scenic cruise along the serene waters of Dubai Creek.\r\nStunning views of iconic landmarks, including Bur Dubai and the historic charm of the Creek.\r\nWarm welcome with refreshing drinks: soft drinks, mineral water, and juices.\r\nLavish international buffet dinner with both vegetarian and non-vegetarian options.\r\nUnlimited refreshments: juice, tea, coffee, and soft drinks.\r\nLive entertainment featuring the dazzling Tanoura dance, an exciting magic show, and a live music program.\r\nBackground music in English, Arabic, and Hindi to set the perfect vibe.\r\nFully air-conditioned lower deck and open-air upper deck for comfort and ambiance.\r\nA smoking area is available on the upper deck for convenience.'),(389,17,'Key tips','Arrive at the marina early to avoid any rush and enjoy the boarding experience.\r\nDress in light and breathable clothes for maximum comfort on both the lower and upper decks.\r\nMake the most of unlimited refreshments like juice, tea, coffee, and soft drinks throughout the cruise.\r\nBring a camera or phone to capture stunning views of Dubai’s iconic landmarks, including Palm Jumeirah, Atlantis, and Burj Al Arab.\r\nTake in the vibrant live Tanoura dance performance and background music for a magical vibe.\r\nSmokers can unwind in the designated smoking area on the upper deck.\r\nExplore both the air-conditioned lower deck and the open-air upper deck for different perspectives of the cruise.\r\nSeparate restroom facilities for men and women ensure a hassle-free and comfortable experience.'),(414,23,'Tour Description','Gear up for the ultimate desert adventure with our Desert Safari with Quad Bike package! Your journey begins with a thrilling ride through the stunning dunes in a 4x4 vehicle, where the beauty of the golden desert surrounds you.\r\nTake it up a notch with an adrenaline-pumping 30-minute quad-biking experience! Feel the excitement as you ride your quad bike across the rugged terrain and sandy slopes—it’s the perfect adventure for thrill-seekers. After all the action, enjoy a camel ride and try sandboarding for even more fun.\r\nAs the sun begins to set, capture breathtaking views of the desert painted in warm hues. At the camp, unwind with a delicious BBQ dinner, refreshing soft drinks, and captivating live performances, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, and a fire show. Add a touch of culture with henna painting or relax with shisha in a cozy setting.\r\nThis package combines non-stop action, cultural experiences, and the peaceful beauty of the desert for a day you’ll always remember.'),(415,23,'Highlights','<h2>Exciting 4x4 dune drive across Red desert sands.</h2><ul><li><p>Adrenaline-filled 30-minute quad biking adventure. Peaceful camel ride for a taste of tradition.</p></li><li><p>Fun sandboarding experience on the dunes.</p></li><li><p>Stunning desert sunset views are perfect for photos.</p></li><li><p>Delicious BBQ dinner with refreshing soft drinks.</p></li><li><p>Spectacular live entertainment, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, and fire shows. Cultural activities like henna painting and relaxing shisha.</p></li></ul><p></p>'),(416,23,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.\r\n'),(417,22,'Tour Description','Escape the city and explore the natural beauty of Hatta on this exciting Hatta mountain tour. Start your day with a pick-up from your residence in Dubai or Sharjah and head towards the stunning landscapes of Hatta.\r\nKick off the adventure with a thrilling desert safari and dune bashing, giving you a taste of Dubai’s rugged side. Then, take in breathtaking views at Hatta View, followed by a visit to the serene Hatta Water Dam, where the turquoise waters contrast beautifully with the surrounding mountains.\r\nStep back in time at Hatta Heritage Village, where you can explore traditional Emirati culture and architecture. Enjoy a stop at Hatta Fort Hotel, a very peaceful retreat in the mountains, before heading to Hatta Hill Park, which is the perfect spot to relax and take in the views.\r\nThe journey continues with a scenic drive through the Al Hajr Mountains, offering stunning landscapes and fresh mountain air. If permitted by military authorities, you may even get the chance to explore Hatta Wadis and freshwater pools offering a refreshing escape.\r\nFinally, after an incredible day of adventure, culture, and nature, you’ll be dropped off back at your residence, bringing this unforgettable tour to a close.'),(418,22,'Highlights','Pick-up from your residence in Dubai, Sharjah or Ajman (8:00 AM to 8:30 AM).\r\nExciting desert safari & dune bashing to kick off the adventure.\r\nPanoramic views at Hatta View showcasing the stunning landscapes.\r\nVisit to Hatta Water Dam, a peaceful spot with stunning turquoise waters.\r\nExplore Hatta Heritage Village to experience the traditions and culture of Arabia.\r\nStop at Hatta Fort Hotel, a charming retreat nestled in the mountains.\r\nRelax at Hatta Hill Park, a scenic spot perfect for unwinding.\r\nDrive through Al Hajr Mountains, offering breathtaking scenery.\r\nExplore Hatta Wadis & fresh water pools (if permitted by military authorities).\r\nDrop-off back at your residence, wrapping up the adventure.'),(419,22,'Key Tips For Your Hatta Mountain Tour','Dress comfortably for outdoor exploration.\r\nStay hydrated and carry a water bottle.\r\nPack essentials like sunglasses, sunscreen, and a hat.\r\nCharge your phone/camera for stunning photos.\r\nRespect local culture at Hatta Heritage Village.\r\nFollow safety guidelines if visiting Wadis or fresh water pools.'),(420,21,'Tour Description','Get ready for a full-day adventure exploring the best of Abu Dhabi! This 12-hour tour gives you a perfect mix of culture, architecture, and entertainment, with the chance to explore one world-class attraction at your own pace.\r\nYour journey starts with pick-up from your hotel, making your trip smooth and stress-free. On the way to Abu Dhabi, you’ll stop at Last Exit, a lively refreshment spot where you can grab a bite or a drink at your own expense.\r\nThe first major highlight is the Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque, one of the most breathtaking mosques in the world. With 82 domes, over 1,000 columns, shimmering chandeliers, and the largest hand-knotted carpet, it’s a must-see masterpiece of architecture.\r\nNext, enjoy a scenic drive past Al Bateen, where luxury hotels overlook the Persian Gulf, and the Corniche promenade offers stunning waterfront views.\r\nThen comes the fun part—you get to choose one attraction to visit:\r\n\r\nAfter soaking in Abu Dhabi’s beauty and excitement, you’ll head back to Dubai, where you’ll be dropped off at your hotel, wrapping up an unforgettable day of exploration.\r\nSince pick-up times can vary by 15-20 minutes due to traffic or road conditions, please be ready in your hotel lobby and let the concierge know you’re waiting for your Arabian Adventures Tour.'),(421,21,'Highlights','Pick-up from your hotel and comfortable transfer to Abu Dhabi.\r\nStop at Last Exit, a fun refreshment spot with food and drink options.\r\nVisit Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque, featuring stunning architecture, golden chandeliers, and the world’s largest hand-knotted carpet.\r\nDrive through Al Bateen, enjoying views of luxury hotels and the scenic Corniche promenade.\r\n\r\nChoice of one attraction:\r\nLouvre Abu Dhabi & Yas Mall – Explore world-class art and enjoy shopping.\r\nWarner Bros. World Abu Dhabi – Enter the world’s largest indoor theme park with exciting rides and cartoon characters.\r\nFerrari World Abu Dhabi – Experience thrilling Ferrari-themed attractions, including the fastest roller coaster in the world.'),(422,21,'Key Tips for Your Abu Dhabi City Tour','	Dress comfortably and modestly.\r\n\r\n	Stay hydrated and carry a water bottle.\r\n\r\n	Respect local customs and etiquette.\r\n\r\n	Bring a camera to capture memorable moments.\r\n\r\n	Use sunscreen and wear a hat.\r\n\r\n	Plan visits around prayer times.\r\n\r\n	Carry local currency (AED).\r\n\r\n'),(423,20,'tour Description','Explore Dubai’s best spots with this city tour designed to give you a real taste of the city’s charm and culture.\r\nStart with pick-up from your hotel or residence, making your journey easy and stress-free. Visit the bustling Gold Souq and Spice Souq, where you can see sparkling jewelry, smell exotic spices, and soak up the local vibe.\r\nNext, stop by Dubai Creek for a quick photo and enjoy a visit to the Dubai Museum, where you’ll learn about the city’s fascinating history. Drive along Jumeirah Road, passing beautiful sights, and stop at the Jumeirah Mosque, a stunning landmark known for its architecture.\r\nTake a photo at Burj Al Arab, one of Dubai’s most famous luxury hotels. Then, head to Palm Jumeirah and Atlantis for another photo-worthy moment that showcases Dubai’s modern achievements.\r\nFinally, drive along the busy Sheikh Zayed Road, where you’ll see Dubai’s impressive skyline filled with towering buildings and unique designs. When the tour ends, we’ll drop you back at your hotel or residence, making sure you finish the day comfortably.\r\nThis package is simple, easy to enjoy, and gives you a true sense of Dubai’s history and modern highlights.'),(424,20,'Highlights','Convenient pick-up and drop-off from your hotel or residence.\r\nVisit the bustling Gold Souq and Spice Souq for a taste of Dubai’s vibrant markets.\r\nPhoto stop at Dubai Creek, a historic and picturesque waterway.\r\nInsightful visit to the Dubai Museum, showcasing the city’s rich history.\r\nScenic drive along Jumeirah Road, passing beautiful cityscapes.\r\nStop at the stunning Jumeirah Mosque, known for its beautiful architecture.\r\nPhoto opportunity at Burj Al Arab, an iconic luxury hotel.\r\nTour of Palm Jumeirah and Atlantis, highlighting Dubai\'s modern achievements.\r\nDrive through Sheikh Zayed Road, with its dazzling skyline of towering skyscrapers.'),(425,20,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Dress comfortably and stay hydrated.\r\nRespect local customs and dress modestly at religious sites.\r\nBring a camera for stunning sights.\r\nUse sunscreen and carry local currency.\r\nPlan visits around opening hours and prayer times.'),(426,19,'Tour Description','Picture this: you’re in the heart of Dubai’s desert, surrounded by towering dunes and a sky full of stars—it’s an experience like no other. With our Overnight Desert Safari, everything is taken care of so you can fully immerse yourself in the magic of the desert.\r\nWe’ll pick you up from your home or hotel in a comfortable 4x4 vehicle and whisk you away to the golden sands. The adventure begins with an exhilarating dune drive, followed by a peaceful camel ride and a fun chance to try sandboarding—it’s a laugh whether you’re a beginner or a pro! As the sun sets, the desert transforms into a photographer’s dream, bathed in warm, golden light.\r\nFor dinner, settle in at our cozy desert camp and enjoy a delicious BBQ meal, freshly cooked just for you, alongside refreshing soft drinks. Sit back and relax while belly dancers, Tanoura performers, and fire artists put on an unforgettable show. But the best part happens later—we’ll set up a private tent just for you on top of a quiet, scenic dune. Imagine sitting by a bonfire with a sky packed with stars and enjoying the cool desert breeze. Comfortable sleeping bags make the whole experience cozy and relaxing.\r\nAs morning comes, wake up to the beauty of sunrise casting its glow across the desert. You’ll enjoy a freshly prepared breakfast before heading back home with memories that will last a lifetime. This isn’t just a safari—it’s your chance to connect with the desert magically.'),(427,19,'Highlights','Convenient pick-up and drop-off in a comfortable 4x4 vehicle.\r\nThrilling dune drive across the golden desert sands.\r\nPeaceful camel ride and fun-filled sandboarding experience.\r\nStunning desert sunset views—perfect for unforgettable photos.\r\nDelicious BBQ dinner with unlimited refreshing drinks.\r\nAmazing live performances, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, and fire shows.\r\nPrivate tent set up on a dune with a cozy bonfire and sleeping bags.\r\nStargazing under a sky full of twinkling stars.\r\nPeaceful morning with a beautiful sunrise and a tasty breakfast.\r\n'),(428,19,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.'),(429,18,'Tour Description','Escape the ordinary and treat yourself to the VIP Desert Safari Dubai experience—designed to make you feel like royalty! We’ll pick you up in a luxury 4x4 vehicle right from your home or hotel so you can relax while we take care of everything.\r\nYour adventure starts with an exciting dune drive, where you’ll glide over the golden desert sands. Then, hop on a camel for a short but memorable ride and give sandboarding a shot—it’s easy, fun, and perfect for beginners. As the sun sets, take a moment to soak in the magic of the desert painted in warm golden hues—a memory you’ll hold onto forever.\r\nWhen it’s time to unwind, you’ll be welcomed into our exclusive VIP lounge. With cozy sofa seating and impeccable service, you’ll feel completely at ease. Enjoy a live BBQ dinner, where delicious dishes are grilled to perfection and paired with unlimited soft drinks. The evening gets even better with mesmerizing live performances, from belly dancing and Tanoura spinning to a jaw-dropping fire show. For a special touch, you can enjoy shisha or get a beautiful henna design crafted by a local artist.\r\nThis VIP Desert Safari Dubai combines thrill, culture, and comfort like no other. It’s not just a tour—it’s an experience you’ll treasure for a lifetime.'),(430,18,'Highlights','Luxury 4x4 pick-up and drop-off from your hotel or residence.\r\nThrilling dune drive across Dubai’s golden desert sands.\r\nCamel ride and sandboarding for a fun and memorable experience.\r\nExclusive VIP lounge access with plush sofa seating.\r\nLive BBQ dinner with freshly grilled dishes and unlimited soft drinks.\r\nMesmerizing live performances, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, fire shows, and more.\r\nRelax with shisha and enjoy henna painting by a skilled artist.\r\nA seamless blend of adventure, culture, and luxury.'),(431,18,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.\r\n'),(432,14,'Full description','Let us take the stress out of planning your desert safari dubai. With our 4x4 pick-up and drop-off, you don’t need to worry about a thing. We’ll pick you up right from your doorstep—your home or hotel—in a luxury vehicle so you can just sit back, relax, and enjoy the ride to the Dubai desert.\r\nOnce you arrive, get ready for an adventure that’s packed with fun! Start with an exciting 4x4 dune drive that’ll have you gliding over the soft sands. Then hop on a camel for a short but memorable ride, and why not give sandboarding a go—it’s easier than it looks! As the day wraps up, you’ll get to watch a stunning sunset paint the desert in warm, golden hues—perfect for capturing on camera.\r\nAfter all the thrills, unwind at our cozy desert camp. Enjoy a delicious BBQ dinner with refreshing drinks, surrounded by a vibrant atmosphere. You’ll love the live performances, from mesmerizing belly dancing to Tanoura spinning and incredible fire shows. Feeling creative? Get a beautiful henna design from a local artist, or simply relax with some shisha.\r\nThis package gives you the best of both worlds: a mix of comfort and adventure, making it a fantastic way to experience Dubai’s desert in style and without any hassle.'),(433,14,'Highlights','Luxury 4x4 pick-up and drop-off right from your hotel or residence.\r\nExciting 4x4 dune drive across Dubai\'s golden desert sands.\r\nMemorable camel ride and fun sandboarding experience.\r\nStunning desert sunset views—perfect for capturing unforgettable moments.\r\nCozy desert camp with a delicious BBQ dinner and refreshing drinks.\r\nLive entertainment, including belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, and fire shows.\r\nHenna painting and relaxing shisha enhance the cultural experience.\r\nA seamless and stress-free way to explore Dubai’s desert in style.'),(434,14,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.\r\n'),(435,13,'Tour Description','Looking for a hassle-free way to explore stunning desert safari dubai? Our Desert Safari with Centralized Bus Pick-Up is the perfect choice. You’ll enjoy comfortable transportation from key locations in the UAE straight to the desert so you can focus on the fun ahead.\r\nOnce there, get ready for an action-packed adventure! Start with an exciting 4x4 dune drive across the golden red sands, followed by a camel ride and a quick sandboarding lesson—both guaranteed to make you smile. And when the sun starts to set, you’re in for a real treat. Watching the desert glow as the sun dips below the horizon is simply magical.\r\nIn the evening, unwind at a traditional desert camp. Enjoy a mouthwatering BBQ dinner and unlimited soft drinks while soaking in the lively atmosphere. Be entertained by mesmerizing belly dancing, Tanoura spinning, fire shows, and other stunning performances. Relax with shisha or treat yourself to beautiful henna designs by a local artist.\r\nThis package has everything you need for a fun and unforgettable Dubai desert safari experience—all without the stress of driving!'),(436,13,'Highlights','Centralized bus pick-up and drop-off from major UAE cities.\r\nThrilling 4x4 dune drive over golden red sands.\r\nCamel riding and sandboarding are fun.\r\nStunning desert sunset views.\r\nRelax at a desert camp with BBQ dinner and drinks.\r\nLive entertainment: belly dancing, Tanoura, fire shows, and more.\r\nHenna painting for an added cultural touch.'),(437,13,'Key Tips for Your Desert Adventure','Wear comfy clothes for running around and exploring, like sneakers and cool, casual outfits.\r\nThe desert can be warm during the day and chilly at night, especially in winter, so bring something cozy just in case.\r\nDon’t forget sunscreen to keep your skin safe from the sun, and pack sunglasses and a hat to stay cool.\r\nIf you have any health concerns or need special help, let the team know, and they’ll do their best to make your adventure fun and safe.\r\nThere are bathrooms available, so you don’t have to worry if nature calls during the trip.\r\nIf you’re pregnant or have certain medical issues, you can skip the bumpy dune drive but still join in on all the other fun activities.\r\nIf you\'re already doing a desert safari and want to sleep under the stars, you can upgrade to an Overnight Safari by chatting with the team on WhatsApp.\r\n');
